ruversionFW.name: ruversionFW
ruversionFW.description: Main firmware version. Format: <code version>H<hardware version>D<date>.

rusysDeviceId.name: rusysDeviceId
rusysDeviceId.description: Remote unit device Id. Each remote unit in a cluster shall have unique ID.

rusysDefOpMode.name: rusysDefOpMode
rusysDefOpMode.description: The operation mode (on or off) the remote unit is on after reboot/power cycle.

rusysActivateOpmode.name: rusysActivateOpmode
rusysActivateOpmode.description: Engage remote unit to on operation mode.

rusysReadCommStr.name: rusysReadCommStr
rusysReadCommStr.description: SNMP agent read community string. It is used for authenticcation purpose.

rusysWriteCommStr.name: rusysWriteCommStr
rusysWriteCommStr.description: SNMP agent write community string. It is used for authentication purpose.

ruswitchesBlockBroadcastMulticast.name: ruswitchesBlockBroadcastMulticast
ruswitchesBlockBroadcastMulticast.description: This switch enables or disables the blocking of Ethernet control packet except ICMP and ARP to reduce the amount of uneccessary overhead introduced to the wireless link.

ruswitchesHTTPD.name: ruswitchesHTTPD
ruswitchesHTTPD.description: When it is turned on, then the remote unit is accessible for configuring via web browser (e.g. IE or Nescape).

ruswitchesAutoScanMasterSignal.name: ruswitchesAutoScanMasterSignal
ruswitchesAutoScanMasterSignal.description: This switch enables or disables the auto scan master unit signal operation on the remote unit only.

rutrafficEthInOctets.name: rutrafficEthInOctets
rutrafficEthInOctets.description: Number of octets of remote unit's payload received on Ethernet port.

rutrafficEthOutOctets.name: rutrafficEthOutOctets
rutrafficEthOutOctets.description: Number of octets of remote unit's payload transmitted on Ethernet port.

rutrafficRfInOctets.name: rutrafficRfInOctets
rutrafficRfInOctets.description: Number of octets of remote unit's payload received from RF port.

rutrafficRfOutOctets.name: rutrafficRfOutOctets
rutrafficRfOutOctets.description: Number of octets of remote unit's payload transmitted to RF port.

rusysTemperature.name: rusysTemperature
rusysTemperature.description: Current remote unit temperature value (in Celsius).

rusysUpdateFlashAndActivate.name: rusysUpdateFlashAndActivate
rusysUpdateFlashAndActivate.description: Save system setting values to Flash and activate the settings.

ruipconfigIpAddress.name: ruipconfigIpAddress
ruipconfigIpAddress.description: New IP address. It will be saved to non-volatile memory and activated in 5 secs.

ruipconfigSubnet.name: ruipconfigSubnet
ruipconfigSubnet.description: New Subnet mask. It will be saved to non-volatile memory and activated in 5 secs.

ruipconfigDefaultGateway.name: ruipconfigDefaultGateway
ruipconfigDefaultGateway.description: New Default gateway. It will be saved to non-volatile memory and activated in 5 secs.

rurftableChannel1.name: rurftableChannel1
rurftableChannel1.description: RF channel 1 frequency (in MHz). It allows you to create your own channel instead of the manufacturing defaults in the remote unit. Keep in mind that channel width is 20MHz, and the frequency specified here is the center frequency. Frequency (5260MHz - 5340MHz) is only applicable to M5830S/P5830S radio.

ruismTxPowerMax.name: ruismTxPowerMax
ruismTxPowerMax.description: The maximum ISM Tx power value can be set (in dBm).

ruismTxPowerMin.name: ruismTxPowerMin
ruismTxPowerMin.description: The minimum ISM Tx power value can be set (in dBm).

ruismTxPower.name: ruismTxPower
ruismTxPower.description: ISM RF tx power (in dBm). It specifies the power output of the radio, excluding the antenna gain. Check parameters remoteismTxPowerMax and remoteismTxPowerMin for power setting range.

ruismRxThreshold.name: ruismRxThreshold
ruismRxThreshold.description: ISM RF rx threshold (in dBm). It specifies the receiver sensitivity of the remote. By default, the radio's sensitivity is -82dBm. The higher the threshold is, the less sensitive the radio will be. In M5800S, the value -90 represents the rfrxthreshold is disabled.

ruuniiTxPowerMax.name: ruuniiTxPowerMax
ruuniiTxPowerMax.description: This object is only applicable to M5830S/P5830S radio. The maximum UNII Tx power value can be set (in dBm).

ruuniiTxPowerMin.name: ruuniiTxPowerMin
ruuniiTxPowerMin.description: This object is only applicable to M5830S/P5830S radio. The minimum UNII Tx power value can be set (in dBm).

ruuniiTxPower.name: ruuniiTxPower
ruuniiTxPower.description: This object is only applicable to M5830S/P5830S radio. UNII RF tx power (in dBm). It specifies the power output of the radio, excluding the antenna gain. Check parameters apuniiTxPowerMax and apuniiTxPowerMin for power setting range.

ruuniiRxThreshold.name: ruuniiRxThreshold
ruuniiRxThreshold.description: This object is only applicable to M5830S/P5830S radio. UNII RF rx threshold (in dBm). It specifies the receiver sensitivity of the master unit.
